gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Cavaliers 140, Wizards 101
gameRecap.excerpt: The Cavaliers defeated the Wizards, 140-101. Max Strus led the way for the Cavaliers with 24 points (6-8 3PT FG), while Donovan Mitchell (22 points) and Caris LeVert (21 points, five rebounds, five assists) added a combined 43 points in the victory. Kyle Kuzma tallied a team-high 16 points for the Wizards in the losing effort. The Cavaliers improve to 19-15 on the season, while the Wizards fall to 6-27.
